notesStmt.note: Written 6 lines per leaf. Accented in red.
Aṣṭaka 8 encompasses folio 1 to folio 155v. Colophon: iti catuhṣaṣṭitamodhyāyah samāptah.

Mahānāmni [Mahānāmnyah] encompasses folio 155v line 3 to folio 158. Colophon: iti samāhānāmnyah samāptah. Samvat 1768 6vaiṣavadi 3 budimadhyenāthaji sadānandajina likhitam. Varga samkhyā 266.
